original_title: Status Quo: The Frantic Four’s Final Fling - Live At The Dublin 02 Arena
overview: When the last notes rang out in the Dublin o2 on Saturday 12 April 2014, the 9000 fans packing the venue knew that they were witness to the end of something special. The reunion that nobody thought would ever be possible did happen, but now the itch was scratched and that particular book was closed.
title: Status Quo: The Frantic Four’s Final Fling - Live At The Dublin 02 Arena
